        <updateDate>2021-07-14T22:34:49Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Marijuana Data Collection Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services, in coordination with the Department of Justice, the Department of Labor, and relevant state agencies, to enter into an arrangement with the National Academy of Sciences in order to study the effects of marijuana legalization in states for medicinal or non-medicinal use.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
