      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To direct the Secretary of Health and Human Services to enter into a 10-year arrangement with the National Academy of Sciences to conduct and update biennially a study on the effects of State legalized marijuana programs, and for other purposes.</title>
